description: Chef Ashraf brings over 20 years of Shawarma-making experience to the streets of Houston and with his royal talents, he’s conquering the appetites of all the hungry locals.The sauces are made fresh, the meats are marinated in a special blend of spices, and only the finest quality ingredients are used to make his entire menu of wonderfully delicious wrapped creations. For a taste of the best Shawerma in Texas, come on out and get your fix of the dish that’s fit for a king!
name: King of Shawerma
